snippet.title: Project Shoreline | Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore, Clean & Restore as a Cute Character in this Cozy Cleaning Mini-Adventure! 🌊
Make sure to subscribe for cozy shorts and more updates ❤ @SpeldosaInteractive 

👉 Play now on Itch.Io — https://speldosainteractive.itch.io/project-shoreline
👉 Report bugs and feedback on our Discord — https://discord.gg/juPPejMsaF

🎵 Music by Tomas Nyman — https://www.instagram.com/noteboy.prod/
